high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the stove
Get the scoop from the cabinet ahead of you
Move to the sink to the right of you
Clean the scoop in the sink and pick it up
Move a few steps away from the sink
But the scoop in the cabinet and close the door
anns.task_desc: Put a scoop in a cabinet.

high_descs: turn right, walk through kitchen, stop at stove, turn to face orange cabinets to the right of the stove
open left cabinet door, pick up ladle with aqua handle, close cabinet door
turn right, walk straight until kitchen sink, stop and face sink
put ladle in sink, wash with water, pick up ladle
back up and open bottom orange cabinet door under the sink on the right
put the ladle inside the cabinet, close the cabinet door
anns.task_desc: pick up a ladle, wash it, place it in a cabinet under sink

high_descs: Walk forward across the room then turn left to face the cabinet above the counter.
Pick up the ladle from the cabinet above the counter.
Turn around and walk forward 2 steps then turn left to face the sink.
Wash the ladle in the sink and pick it back up.
Step back and face the cabinet on the right side under the sink.
Place the ladle in the right most cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Wash a ladle and store it in the cabinet on the right, under the sink.
